-Didn't I tell you I disliked the room?

142
00:11:11,379 --> 00:11:13,005
Come on, look at me.

143
00:11:14,173 --> 00:11:15,508
That's enough.

144
00:11:17,385 --> 00:11:19,220
I practically pay your wage, remember?

145
00:11:19,303 --> 00:11:20,971
You brat.

146
00:11:22,014 --> 00:11:23,474
Give it a rest, okay?

147
00:11:23,974 --> 00:11:25,059
You've done enough.

148
00:11:25,726 --> 00:11:26,852
You can leave now.

149
00:11:26,936 --> 00:11:28,562
Stop it already, you two.

150
00:11:28,646 --> 00:11:29,605
You should get going.

151
00:11:29,688 --> 00:11:30,648
Don't stick around.

152
00:11:39,115 --> 00:11:40,908
-That might be the end of him.
-Who? Your pal?

153
00:11:40,991 --> 00:11:42,827
No, your pal, you idiot.

154
00:11:42,910 --> 00:11:44,620
