It's 40,000 won.

184
00:14:13,978 --> 00:14:16,981
What? It's… 40,000 won?

185
00:14:17,064 --> 00:14:19,275
Oh, no.

186
00:14:20,985 --> 00:14:23,612
Just a second.

187
00:14:27,283 --> 00:14:30,411
Do you perhaps take bus tokens?

