-Oh, no…

201
00:15:12,369 --> 00:15:13,370
Oh, my gosh.

202
00:15:13,454 --> 00:15:14,914
Are you okay, Tae-poong?

203
00:15:14,997 --> 00:15:16,540
-Oh, you poor boy.
-I'm fine.

204
00:15:16,624 --> 00:15:17,583
-You, Tae-poong!
-Yes?

205
00:15:17,666 --> 00:15:19,919
